00:45.246 --> 00:47.146
Is there a problem?

00:47.148 --> 00:48.514
You got excessive
noise, loitering...

00:48.516 --> 00:50.449
my feet are moving.
Not me--

00:50.451 --> 00:52.151
Peter, come on!

00:52.153 --> 00:54.253
I was talking
to the policeman.
Where are you going?

00:54.255 --> 00:56.155
The car's over there.
We got to go home.

00:56.157 --> 00:57.156
At midnight?
Come on.

00:57.158 --> 00:59.158
Let's go to Nirvana.

00:59.159 --> 01:01.159
It's time to go home, Peter.
It's not time
to go home.

01:01.162 --> 01:02.394
Give me a kiss.

01:02.396 --> 01:05.164
I don't want
to give you a kiss.

01:05.166 --> 01:06.398
