01:18.412 --> 01:20.479
Lois Ryder, 16 East 85.

01:20.481 --> 01:22.381
Off the park. Nice.

01:22.383 --> 01:24.116
Saperstein, 3-6.

01:24.118 --> 01:26.368
Phil Cerreta,
Mike Logan.

01:26.369 --> 01:28.619
What's the matter, you
don't get enough work
in your own turf?

01:28.622 --> 01:31.623
Hit her in the head,
maybe a baseball bat?

