with it?

12:48.335 --> 12:52.003
Look, this thing
with Dr. Friedman--

12:52.005 --> 12:54.472
my wife and I discussed it.

12:54.474 --> 12:56.207
It was ending...

12:56.209 --> 12:58.476
and frankly,
i don't think

12:58.478 --> 13:01.246
