the speech when we get home?"

14:42.582 --> 14:44.949
Me, I say they ought
to get shot.

14:44.951 --> 14:48.019
Ryder knew
about the mugger.

14:48.021 --> 14:50.188
Thanks a lot.

14:50.190 --> 14:53.057
Now we know why he didn't want
to take the blood test.

14:53.059 --> 14:55.193
He didn't want us
to look for the boyfriend.

14:55.195 --> 14:57.996
